# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Whitelist strategy: ignore everything, then re-include the reusable files.
# This is intentional. The ~/.claude directory is full of secrets, caches,
# and machine-specific state. It is far safer to opt files IN than to chase
# down every transient file that should be opted out.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Ignore everything by default
/*

# --- Re-include the things worth sharing across machines ---

# Repo metadata
!/.gitignore

# Global instructions + any Markdown includes imported by CLAUDE.md
# (e.g. memory-routing.md, spin-down-quiz.md). Whitelisting all root-level
# .md means future includes are shared automatically. Secrets can't slip in
# here — they're .key/.env/.jsonl and are re-ignored in the section below.
!/*.md

# Settings: share the sanitized base config, never the secret key file.
# The API key is read by settings.json's apiKeyHelper from .anthropic-key,
# which stays gitignored. Share the template instead.
!/settings.json
!/.anthropic-key.example

# Reusable building blocks
!/commands/
!/skills/
!/hooks/

# Notification hook scripts (code is shareable; runtime state is not)
!/claude-notifications/
/claude-notifications/state.json

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Belt-and-suspenders: even if a directory above gets re-included, make sure
# these never slip in regardless of where they appear.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Secrets / local overrides
.anthropic-key
settings.local.json
settings.json.backup
*.key
*.pem
.env
.env.*

# Conversation + usage history (often contains pasted secrets, code, PII)
history.jsonl
**/*.jsonl

# Caches and transient runtime state
cache/
shell-snapshots/
session-env/
sessions/
focus-state/
file-history/
ide/
.last-cleanup

# Project-local transcripts and per-project state
projects/
plans/

# Plugin caches (marketplace clones, install counts, etc.)
plugins/

# Backups (the .claude.json backups embed the API key and full config)
backups/

# OS / editor noise
.DS_Store
*.swp
*~
